{"tid":1632214,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港轉咗入大直路啦，唔係依家先黎炒嘛？","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:45:07.000Z","uid":110332,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca959c8dd31a0145b400494d509c45e212b5437","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實我地已經攬炒緊，可能有人問攬炒幾時由手段變咗目的，但係事實係，如果佢俾唔到民主，我地就攬炒，依家就係佢話俾唔到，所以就要攬炒！</span></span>釐清目的之後，就講下以後嘅做法！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先，團結！不割！有不滿用補鑊方式多於屌！</span></span> 我地正正就係不割先可以行到依家！！小心風向撚，有咩都好！我地幫手補鑊！但永遠不會割，永遠支持！依個<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係盲撐</span></span></strong>，我地補鑊就代表我地知做得不足，但一定會繼續支持，因為佢地嘅初心同我地一樣！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />文宣緊急法=想做咩都得=隨時有權沒收任何人財產</span></span>仲記得當初有人反對佢出緊急法，因為樓價會狂跌，但依家仲未跌，點解？就係因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個市仲好多人都唔知緊急法嘅意思，仲對個市好有信心！但其實林鄭同稱咗帝冇分別</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />休戰並等待美國人權法通過，其間養精蓄銳，討論人權法過咗嘅下一步升級</span></span>因為港共一定會係通過咗之後有動靜！到時就同佢黎鑊金嘅！(方法可以留言討論，但依家真係要休息同準備下)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">讓子彈飛一陣，我地做完野要等佢發酵，睇埋發酵完點再行下一步！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人反抗！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0bf2ea17802db849bdc0d32a60c05faa9b6203bd","tid":1632214,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長文][召喚全世界] 嘈完就入黎 睇下下一步應該做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55e1a24370e0dfa034f393d4fe9d24cf0987d0fd","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，繼續推向攬炒</span>"},{"pid":"69adc2f7aa6b8c14e3f359562ddc66b1bec858c0","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，繼續推向攬炒</span>"},{"pid":"87b7f33ca4d4ffbba727eb247d85beed05bd885a","tid":1632214,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">無理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">8964</span>, 之後被國際制裁<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">合理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">新彊</span>, 然後就沒有了然後"},{"pid":"ba6ca2965c34ab4f21fddf216caadf4ec511de6d","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"0ec98ef5cb4370e0a02cc4991da599ac89edfc9b","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b7f33ca4d4ffbba727eb247d85beed05bd885a","tid":1632214,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:19:31.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">無理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">8964</span>, 之後被國際制裁<br />\n中共<span style=\"color: red;\">合理</span>出老解, <span style=\"color: red;\">新彊</span>, 然後就沒有了然後"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:52.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推！"},{"pid":"eebfc458fd56ceee225587d66bcbaabd471e4a6b","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bf2ea17802db849bdc0d32a60c05faa9b6203bd","tid":1632214,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[長文][召喚全世界] 嘈完就入黎 睇下下一步應該做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:03.000Z","msg":"互推！"},{"pid":"5f21a620aeb16d429fa187b47a09b5f8e3b5cd42","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"d73a51d9fb9e40383b97fb466a71a5ee0b2baf93","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"ce8faeacdd47f18834d8101d0d64e04e4084c616","tid":1632214,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"3c04541ad010264807d582db787d5ef00b66f58a","tid":1632214,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"裝修暫時停工<br />\n18區唱歌歡迎人權法"},{"pid":"b877ccc2aba810e4e76e018c856d60669400cba2","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c04541ad010264807d582db787d5ef00b66f58a","tid":1632214,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:58.000Z","msg":"裝修暫時停工<br />\n18區唱歌歡迎人權法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"d160e7685ceca1584a5a6f661ce932c2e6eb21e1","tid":1632214,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep