;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"e7df9ba2a32722d36e659ad99cef5f9bb56aeb0b","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d160e7685ceca1584a5a6f661ce932c2e6eb21e1","tid":1632214,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span>"},{"pid":"947074d7a16936dfc678371dcd2cf75e858a7266","tid":1632214,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n團結"},{"pid":"3259c2fdda3e858cd4be70c234314ddefbbb5b8e","tid":1632214,"uid":110332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"947074d7a16936dfc678371dcd2cf75e858a7266","tid":1632214,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:35:14.000Z","msg":"岩<br />\n團結"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:36:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣緊急法，勇武養精蓄銳，永遠不會割不屌，只會補鑊！</span><br />\n<br />\n香港轉咗入大直路啦，唔係依家先黎炒嘛？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632214\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632214</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"